## Quick reference — common failure modes

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------|-----|
| `git push` rejected, tag ambiguity | Remote `prod` tag exists | `git push origin :refs/tags/prod` first |
| `--force-with-lease` rejected | Remote has commits not in local `prod` | `git fetch origin prod && git log prod..origin/prod` |
| Sidecar shows old commit after restart | gitclone loop hasn't fired yet | Wait 60s or exec into sidecar and run `git pull origin prod` manually |
| `/var/www/ood/apps/sys/bc_opencode/` empty | emptyDir not yet populated | Sidecar init container may still be running; check pod events |
